        <akn:num>16-3703</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Affidavit; contents.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_16-3703_1">
      <akn:num>(1)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>according to affiantâ€™s information and belief, the plaintiff is entitled to recover possession of chattels proposed to be replevied, being the same described in the complaint;</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_16-3703_2">
      <akn:num>(2)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>the defendant has seized and detained or detains the chattels; and</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_16-3703_3">
      <akn:num>(3)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>the chattels were not subject to the seizure or detention and were not taken upon a writ of replevin between the parties.</akn:p></akn:content>
